<p>iPadOS 26 introduced a new windowing system, improved audio recording, and more robust background tasks, making the iPad feel more Mac-like than ever. On this episode of <em>Mac Power Users</em>, Stephen and I discuss <a href="https://www.relay.fm/mpu/824" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">a range of workflows that benefit from these changes</span></a>.</p>



